name: AVCaptureResolvedPhotoSettings
desc: A description of the features and settings in use for an in-progress or complete photo capture request.

items.name: var uniqueID: Int64
items.desc: The unique identifier for the photo capture this settings object corresponds to.

items.name: var expectedPhotoCount: Int
items.desc: The number of photo capture results in the capture request.

items.name: var isFlashEnabled: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value indicating whether the camera flash fires for this capture.

items.name: var isRedEyeReductionEnabled: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value indicating whether the camera automatically reduces red-eye when capturing photos.

items.name: var isVirtualDeviceFusionEnabled: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that specifies whether the system automatically uses virtual device image fusion.

items.name: var isContentAwareDistortionCorrectionEnabled: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the system applies content-aware distortion correction when capturing the photo.

items.name: var photoDimensions: CMVideoDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the photo image (in a processed format, such as JPEG) that the capture delivers.

items.name: var rawPhotoDimensions: CMVideoDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the RAW-format photo image that the capture delivers.

items.name: var previewDimensions: CMVideoDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the preview image that the system delivers with the capture.

items.name: var embeddedThumbnailDimensions: CMVideoDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the thumbnail image that the capture delivers.

items.name: var rawEmbeddedThumbnailDimensions: CMVideoDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the RAW-format embedded thumbnail image that the capture delivers.

items.name: var livePhotoMovieDimensions: CMVideoDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the Live Photo movie content that the capture delivers.

items.name: var portraitEffectsMatteDimensions: CMVideoDimensions
items.desc: The size, in pixels, of the portrait effects matte that the capture delivers.

items.name: func dimensionsForSemanticSegmentationMatte(ofType: AVSemanticSegmentationMatte.MatteType) -> CMVideoDimensions
items.desc: Retrieves the resolved dimensions of the semantic segmentation mattes that the photo output delivers.

items.name: var photoProcessingTimeRange: CMTimeRange
items.desc: The time range in which to expect the system to deliver the photo to the delegate.
